OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFree week in Rhodes for    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fevacuated tourists - Greek 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FPM                         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Greek prime minister has pledged to
OL,6, give tourists who had to escape the    
OL,7, recent wildfires on the island of      
OL,8, Rhodes a free one-week holiday there.  
OL,10,FSpeaking on ITV's Good Morning Britain,
OL,11,FKyriakos Mitsotakis said people could  
OL,12,Ftake up the offer in the spring or     
OL,13,Fautumn of 2024.                        
OL,15,FBut he did not give details of how the 
OL,16,Ffree week could be claimed, or how the 
OL,17,Fscheme would work.                     
OL,19,FMore than 20,000 people were evacuated 
OL,20,Fwhen wildfires broke out in July.      
